{"title":"Say goodbye to dropped smart trainer connections with Wahoo’s Kickr Direct Connect","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/wahoo-kickr-direct-connect/","date":1611666000000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=45&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1920,1278 1920w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-3-8b962ef.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-614398 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"Wahoo Direct Connect dongle\" title=\"Wahoo Direct Connect dongle\" />                                            \n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Wahoo has just released the Kickr Direct Connect dongle, a £79.99 piece of hardware that plugs into a Kickr <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-smart-trainer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">smart trainer</a> for a wired ethernet connection into your home network.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/wahoo/\">Wahoo</a> says that it’s aimed at users who have problems with wireless connectivity to the internet and experience drop-outs while riding. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">“While a wireless connection works very well for most riders, those who have connectivity challenges, or those who simply cannot risk a dropout during an important race or workout will be able to ride with increased confidence and reliability by using Kickr Direct Connect,” says Wahoo’s Tyler Harris.</span></p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Wahoo-Direct-Connect-4-c89921b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/producti